        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer181001638" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2697485135453873828">I truly loved this whole trilogy. My book club started with the third book in the series, and I loved it so much that I HAD to read the other two. Each one is set during the civil war and each story is told from different view points during parallel times. One time we read about a slave owner and her slaves. Another book covers a slave owner who is sympathetic to the slaves and helps them. And the third book covers a young girl who serves in the war. All the characters cross over with each other</span>
  <span id="freeText2697485135453873828" style="display:none">I truly loved this whole trilogy. My book club started with the third book in the series, and I loved it so much that I HAD to read the other two. Each one is set during the civil war and each story is told from different view points during parallel times. One time we read about a slave owner and her slaves. Another book covers a slave owner who is sympathetic to the slaves and helps them. And the third book covers a young girl who serves in the war. All the characters cross over with each other in all the books. I loved the character development and fell in love with the characters. Another favorite part of mine is how the author is not afraid to share the characters' belief in Christ. I couldn't put the books down and would highly recommend them to anyone. There is history, emotion, drama and even a little bit of romance. </span>
  <a data-text-id="2697485135453873828" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


